<?xml version="1.0"?>
<section xml:id="active-code_html">
  <title>HTML</title>
  <p>Teaching a class on HTML and simple web design?  Why not use activecode for HTML too?
            Although you don't run HTML, clicking the run button will cause the HTML to be rendered.</p>
  <program xml:id="html1" interactive="activecode" language="htmlmixed">
    <input>
&lt;html&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;style&gt;
    h2 { font-size: 48px;
         color: red;
    }
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Hello World&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;one&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;two&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
        </input>
  </program>
  <hint>
    <program language="rst">
      <input>
